				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Now recruiting:  Please submit your resume for consideration.<a name="59055"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 26 04 2:13 AM</span></td>
